Are you hungry?
You'll starve to death.

85
00:11:53,479 --> 00:11:57,108
Well, today l got 20 rupees
from a rich man.

86
00:11:59,151 --> 00:12:03,110
His car was run over a woman's leg.
l gave false witness for him.

87
00:12:05,491 --> 00:12:09,450
Shyam, remember how you found
a lame sparrow as a kid?

88
00:12:11,997 --> 00:12:14,465
You cared for it
until it was better.

89
00:12:14,934 --> 00:12:16,902
l was only a kid.

90
00:12:19,672 --> 00:12:21,640
But you are a kid now also.

91
00:13:29,942 --> 00:13:33,810
''Lament not...''

92
00:13:35,014 --> 00:13:41,647
''if l turn my face away...''

93
00:13:43,956 --> 00:13:48,655
''your gaze is filled...''

94
00:13:48,794 --> 00:13:52,821
''with such longing''

95
00:13:57,803 --> 00:13:59,270
Listen.

96
00:14:04,643 --> 00:14:05,940
l was saying...

97
00:14:07,146 --> 00:14:10,274
''Who know what you said?''

98
00:14:11,317 --> 00:14:14,445
''Who knows what l heard?''

99
00:14:15,154 --> 00:14:18,123
''Something stirred in my heart''

100
00:14:19,558 --> 00:14:22,288
''Who knows what you said...?''

101
00:14:58,297 --> 00:15:05,100
''l felt my heart awaken,
l felt such elation''

102
00:15:13,979 --> 00:15:20,441
''Slumbering dreams reawakened,
something stirred in my heart''

103
