''Something stirred in my heart''

106
00:15:57,623 --> 00:16:04,426
''l stumble no more,
my feet no longer falter''

107
00:16:13,472 --> 00:16:19,604
''There is new life in my step.
Something stirred in my heart''

108
00:16:20,646 --> 00:16:23,774
''Who knows what you said''

