''lf your head reels with pain,
or your heart sinks in gloom...''

206
00:31:56,147 --> 00:32:02,609
''Don't fret, leave it to me;
l'll set things right soon''

207
00:32:03,988 --> 00:32:05,615
''Massage, oil massage!''

208
00:32:31,883 --> 00:32:35,979
''The lotion l use has magic.
Curing baldness and dandruff"

209
00:32:36,521 --> 00:32:40,821
''Once my hands begin to whirl,
your hair won't look so rough''

210
